elements.name: Get the information in the database

steps.name: Prenez toutes les villes avec ses pays "SELECT city.city_id,city.city,country.country FROM city LEFT JOIN country ON city.country_id=country.country_id"

arguments.val: SELECT city.city_id,city.city,country.country FROM city LEFT JOIN country ON city.country_id=country.country_id

steps.name: Prenez tous les clients et ses address "SELECT customer_id, first_name, last_name, address, district FROM customer LEFT JOIN address ON  customer.address_id=address.address_id ORDER BY district"

arguments.val: SELECT customer_id, first_name, last_name, address, district FROM customer LEFT JOIN address ON  customer.address_id=address.address_id ORDER BY district

steps.name: Trouvez combien de films id de acteur a "SELECT actor_id, count(title) FROM film_actor LEFT JOIN film ON film.film_id=film_actor.film_id GROUP BY actor_id;"

arguments.val: SELECT actor_id, count(title) FROM film_actor LEFT JOIN film ON film.film_id=film_actor.film_id GROUP BY actor_id;
